sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant HTTP as Caikit Runtime<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as Caikit Runtime<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant TextGen as TextGeneration<br/>(Local Module)
    participant PeftTGIS as PeftPromptTuningTGIS<br/>(Remote Module)
    participant Embed as EmbeddingModule<br/>(sentence-transformers)
    participant PyTorch as Local PyTorch Model<br/>(GPU/CPU)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Backend<br/>gRPC (configurable port)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 1: Local Text Generation Inference

    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>Auth: None (platform-dependent)
    HTTP->>TextGen: In-process dispatch
    TextGen->>PyTorch: Forward pass (generate)
    PyTorch-->>TextGen: Generated tokens
    TextGen-->>HTTP: GeneratedTextResult
    HTTP-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 2: Remote TGIS Text Generation (with PEFT)

    Client->>gRPC: TextGenerationTaskService.Generate<br/>Auth: None (platform-dependent)
    gRPC->>PeftTGIS: In-process dispatch
    PeftTGIS->>TGIS: gRPC GenerationRequest<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    TGIS-->>PeftTGIS: GenerationResponse
    PeftTGIS-->>gRPC: GeneratedTextResult
    gRPC-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 3: Streaming Text Generation (Remote TGIS)

    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/server-streaming-text-generation
    HTTP->>PeftTGIS: In-process dispatch (streaming)
    PeftTGIS->>TGIS: gRPC ServerStreamingGenerate<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    loop Stream tokens
        TGIS-->>PeftTGIS: GenerationResponse (token)
        PeftTGIS-->>HTTP: GeneratedTextStreamResult
        HTTP-->>Client: SSE token chunk
    end

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 4: Text Embedding Inference

    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/embedding<br/>Auth: None (platform-dependent)
    HTTP->>Embed: In-process dispatch
    Embed->>PyTorch: SentenceTransformer.encode()
    PyTorch-->>Embed: Embedding vectors
    Embed-->>HTTP: EmbeddingResult
    HTTP-->>Client: JSON Response (vectors)

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 5: Model Loading (on startup)

    gRPC->>TextGen: Load model
    TextGen->>HFHub: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 (if allow_downloads=true)
    HFHub-->>TextGen: Model weights + config
    TextGen->>PyTorch: Load into GPU/CPU memory
    PyTorch-->>TextGen: Model ready
